name: python-keystoneclient
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "python-keystoneclient" %}
{% set version = "3.22.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 6e2b6d2a5ae5d7aa26d4e52d1c682e08417d2c5d73ccc54cb65c54903a868cb4

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pbr
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - debtcollector
    - keystoneauth1
    - oslo.config
    - oslo.i18n
    - oslo.serialization
    - oslo.utils
    - pbr
    - python
    - requests
    - setuptools
    - six
    - stevedore

test:
  imports:
    - keystoneclient

about:
  home: https://github.com/openstack/python-keystoneclient
  license: Apache Software
  license_family: APACHE
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "Client Library for OpenStack Identity"
  doc_url: https://docs.openstack.org/python-keystoneclient/latest/
  dev_url: https://opendev.org/openstack/python-keystoneclient

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
